---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<Layout 
    title="Publicidad en Google y Meta Ads | SEMTIC" 
    description="Campañas digitales en Google AdWords, Facebook Ads e Instagram. Aparece exactamente donde tus clientes te están buscando."
    image="https://semtic.cl/og-servicios.png">

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center pt-32 pb-20 overflow-hidden" style="z-index: 10;">
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-64 md:w-96 h-64 md:h-96 bg-[#39ff14] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-pulse"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-64 md:w-96 h-64 md:h-96 bg-[#00f2ea] rounded-full mix-blend-screen filter blur-[128px] opacity-20 animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s;"></div>

        <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-4 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
                Publicidad en Google y <span class="text-gradient">Meta Ads</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10 font-light leading-relaxed">
                Campañas rentables, hiper-segmentadas y focalizadas en maximizar el retorno de tu inversión publicitaria.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Beneficios -->
    <section class="py-24 relative" style="z-index: 10; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.3), rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.6));">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
                <div class="space-y-8">
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6">
                        No gastes dinero, <span class="text-gradient">inviértelo con inteligencia</span>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        Gestionamos eficientemente tus anuncios en Google y redes sociales para que tus ofertas lleguen directo a los usuarios con la mayor intención de compra.
                    </p>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#39ff14] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#39ff14] shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-gray-400">Google Ads (Search): Aparece de primero cuando te busquen.</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#39ff14] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#39ff14] shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-gray-400">Meta Ads (Facebook e Instagram): Alcanza audiencias similares y genera demanda.</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 mt-2 bg-[#39ff14] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_10px_#39ff14] shrink-0"></span>
                            <span class="text-gray-400">Retargeting: Convierte a las visitas previas que aún no han comprado.</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="relative p-10 rounded-3xl bg-[#0a0a1a]/40 border border-white/5 backdrop-blur-md">
                   <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#39ff14]/10 to-transparent opacity-100 rounded-3xl"></div>
                   <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] relative z-10">¿Por qué anunciarte con nosotros?</h3>
                   <ul class="space-y-6 relative z-10">
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-[#39ff14]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[#39ff14]">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-gray-300">Enfoque 100% en ventas y leads, no solo métricas de vanidad.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-[#39ff14]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[#39ff14]">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-gray-300">Optimización diaria del Costo por Adquisición (CPA).</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-white/10 pb-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-[#39ff14]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[#39ff14]">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-gray-300">Transparencia y acceso total a tus cuentas publicitarias.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-center gap-4">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded bg-[#39ff14]/20 flex items-center justify-center text-[#39ff14]">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 5H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v11a2 2 0 002 2h11a2 2 0 002-2v-5m-1.414-9.414a2 2 0 112.828 2.828L11.828 15H9v-2.828l8.586-8.586z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-gray-300">Creación de copys (textos) persuasivos e imágenes de alto impacto.</span>
                        </li>
                   </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Final -->
    <section class="py-20 relative" style="z-index: 10; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.8), rgba(5, 5, 17, 0.95));">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-[family-name:var(--font-space-grotesk)] font-bold mb-6">
                Lleva tráfico cualificado a <span class="text-gradient">tus ofertas</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-400 mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
                No desperdicies tu presupuesto sin saber qué funciona. Cotiza ahora tu campaña publicitaria y haz que tu anuncio se posicione.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
                <a href="https://wa.me/56988169404?text=Hola,%20quisiera%20más%20información%20sobre%20publicidad%20en%20Google%20y%20Meta%20Ads" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center px-10 py-5 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#25D366] to-[#39ff14] rounded-full text-[#050511] font-extrabold text-lg tracking-wide shadow-lg hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(37,211,102,0.5)] transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Agenda una reunión por WhatsApp
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

</Layout>
